  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nThis shows that effectiveBalance is always multiples of 1Eth and should not be more than 32Eth: https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/b49ac4c084c21be52cd9b98e2151c18851b5af73/packages/beacon-state-transition/src/allForks/epoch/processEffectiveBalanceUpdates.ts#L26\r\n\r\na confirmation of effective balance in mainnet: the value set is like `@@@ effectiveBalances of all validators Set(3) { 32000000000, 31000000000, 30000000000 }`\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nWe should be able to avoid recalculating rewards and penalties by using a cache to help:\r\n+ improve state transition speed\r\n+ save memory due to BigInt calculation\r\n\r\ncurrent situation in Prater shows that it may take more than 1s to process rewards and penalties\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1089\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-07-12 at 08 38 55\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/125218258-ba425280-e2ec-11eb-94d4-1d91ae04021b.png\">\r\n",
